          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". That’s what the owner of a 1980 Chevy Camaro Berlinetta has been facing since the muscle car was spray painted over Labor Day weekend. When the owner went to his shop, instead of the beautiful original paint, he found lewd messages and images.",
